'''Lex Lang''' is an American voice actor and director who voiced [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] in the games ''[[Star Wars: Battlefront II]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike]]''. He is the official "audio double" for the character played by [[Harrison Ford]]. He was also "Stormtrooper 1" in ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]'' and [[Poe Dameron]] in ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Resistance Rises]]''. He provided additional voices in ''[[Rogue One: A Star Wars Story]].''

